        "bullet_point": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "POLICE BADGE HOLDER WALLET: The badge holder is designed for private and public security professionals who at times require discretion of their ID for undercover, covert or plainclothes operations; the wallet features a compact design that includes a removable ID card holder, a cash compartment, credit card slots, a suede badge protection flap and recessed badge cut-out mount",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "REMOVABLE ID CARD HOLDER: The wallet includes a compact and removable ID card holder that easily slides in or out from the center of the leather bifold wallet, giving you ample space for other cards, photos and more; the ID card holder also helps to shield badges from sight, adding another layer of discretion",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "SUEDE BADGE PROTECTION FLAP: The police badge holder and ID card holder features a built in suede badge protection flap to keep badges scratch free and more importantly, hidden from view if necessary in covert field situations",
