        "product_description": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "The ASR Federal Black Leather Police Bifold Wallet Badge Holder has been designed for private and public security professionals, who at times, require discretion of their ID for undercover, covert or plainclothes operations. The wallet features a compact design that includes a removable ID card holder, a cash compartment, credit card slots, an interior suede badge protection flap and recessed badge cut-out mount. <br/><br/>Made from 100% genuine leather, this badge holder wallet boasts a strong and sturdy construction with reinforced stitching and a heavy gauge leather body; the badge holder will relax over time with use as it molds to your carrying habits, but will never forego its integrity and structure. Furthermore, the removable ID card holder that easily slides in or out from the center of the bifold wallet, giving you ample space for other cards, photos and more; the ID card holder also helps to shield badges from sight, adding another layer of discretion. Lastly, the police badge holder and ID card holder features a built in suede badge protection flap to keep badges scratch free and more importantly, hidden from view if necessary in covert field situations.<br/><br/>Badge attachment is clip-back, no screws required. This wallet is specifically designed for an oval-shaped badge (Maximum Badge Size: 3 3/8 x 2 1/4 inches); badge wallet holders for shield or round badges are available.<br/><br/>NOTE: Badge is NOT included with purchase; Please be sure to measure YOUR specific badge to ensure it fits this wallet",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
            ],
            "is_required": true,
            "source": "catalog",
            "asin": "B01M18PHNU",
            "raw_value": true
        },
